{"tid":640515,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立會擬禁煲底set大台","createTime":"2018-04-24T10:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T10:28:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"547817f1a138d1758c4433e4f48e2378740d216b","tid":640515,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:26:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180424/20371193?_ga=2.79400596.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F20371193%3F_ga%3D2.79400596.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=PIhFHYhkq2G3Nufb4QOKIbr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=4c4de0b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F20371193%3F_ga%3D2.79400596.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=2ac171bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180424/20371193?_ga=2.79400596.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月24日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：戴耀廷餘波　立會擬禁煲底set大台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180424/large/18674700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180424%2Flarge%2F18674700.jpg&h=b2e367d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民主派立法會議員本月7日晚喺立法會示威區（俗稱煲底）舉辦千人集會，聲援戴耀廷同香港嘅言論自由。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n民主派立法會議員本月7日晚聯同民陣喺立法會示威區（俗稱煲底）舉辦千人集會，聲援被建制派圍剿嘅港大副教授戴耀廷同香港嘅言論自由，當晚公民黨郭家麒為集會搭建舞台同豎立背板，遭立法會行管會警告，原來事件仲有餘波，行管會擬修改立法會示威區指引，禁止豎立任何舞台或背幕。<br />\n<br />\n行管會透過立法會秘書處就修改「立法會廣場使用指引」諮詢議員，信中提及本月初集會豎立咗一個超出限制嘅舞台連背幕，行管會認為基於安全理由要修改指引，規定日後示威區內唔准豎設任何舞台或舞台連背景，或秘書處認為會對示威區人士構成安全危險嘅臨時構築物喎，議員要喺本周五前提出意見。指引仲訂明，若示威人士唔遵守指引，立法會行管會可拒絕有關人士進入示威區或要求佢哋離開，並可採取法律訴訟行動㖭噃。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：落區被點錯相　AY變袋巾 (李八方)"},{"pid":"823aae6e2252db83e8f7bd2d3cedd4c2d2119f6a","tid":640515,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:28:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/182844_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F182844_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=9d0f8333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"}]}